 Pat. And Bear Stearns had a big investor conference, a couple thousand peo=
ple in the audience, and there was a public debate of RISC versus CISC at t=
he time, of John versus Pat.

And I start laying out the dogma of instruction set compatibility, architec=
tural coherence, how software always becomes the determinant of any compute=
r architecture being developed. =E2=80=9CSoftware follows instruction set. =
Instruction set follows Moore=E2=80=99s Law. And unless you=E2=80=99re 10X =
better and John, you=E2=80=99re not 10X better, you=E2=80=99re lucky if you=
