cause architectural compatibility becomes so dominant in the adoption of an=
y new computer platform.=E2=80=9D And this is when x86=E2=80=93 there was n=
o server x86. There=E2=80=99s no clouds at this point in time. And John and=
 I got into this big public debate and it was so popular.

