uman capabilities across all cognitive domains and would surpass the sharpe=
st human minds at every task. Among the specific actions the Commission
recommends for Congress:

* Provide broad multiyear contracting authority to the executive branch and=
 associated funding for leading artificial intelligence, cloud, and data ce=
nter companies and others to advance the stated policy at a pace and scale =
